features: 【Company Philosophy】Our passion is to capture the essence and cultural spirit of these classics, which are replica models of iconic classic micro-aircraft from different eras. Every detail is a testament to our passion for creativity and superior craftsmanship, ensuring each miniature model aircraft is a true work of art.

Our aircraft models are made of imported zinc alloy raw materials, die-cast and forged, which are elastic and can resist deformation and damage even when impacted. Thanks to the electrostatic coating, the surface is exquisitely crafted and displays a gloss similar to the original body color.

The rich details add reliability and collectability to this miniature iconic aircraft model, providing a stunning visual experience that satisfies the passion and expectations for aviation collection. While admiring the aircraft's take-off state, you will be fascinated by its charm.

Crafted with craftsmanship, experience the true beauty. Silver plated to make a meaningful gift and treasured collectible, this realistic aerospace model's miniature size can be placed on tabletops and display cases for decorative display, adding a touch of sophistication.

【Service After Sales】In addition to a rich collection of classic aerospace models, we also offer a variety of automobile scale models. Whether you are an experienced collector or a fan who appreciates the miraculous beauty of these miniatures, we invite you to explore their mysteries together and we value your feedback and suggestions.
